- Added "deage" shop item:
  - Adds 8 new endings:
    - "Young" and "Young (Female)"
    - "Young (Drunk)" and "Young (Drunk Female)"
        - You require beer

    - "Young (First)" and "Young (Female First)"
        - Only if you don't have any of the following:
            - "Young"
            - "Young (Female)"
            - "Young (Drunk)"
            - "Young (Drunk Female)"
            - "Young (First)"
            - "Young (Female First)"
        - And if you are about to unlock:
            - "Young"
            - "Young (Female)"

    - "Young (The Hard Way)" && "Young (Female The Hard Way)"
        - Only if you don't have, but are about to unlock the following:
            - "Young"
            - "Young (Female)"

- The Anti-Autoclicker goal penalty is now gradual
- You can now exceed max Autoclicker violations again
- The win state sprite is shifted down
- Aurora's tolerance drains now at the same rate as aurora's annoyance
- The temp noise that plays when you click on aurora now has a random pitch
